e vowel becomes nasalized to mimic the nasal sound of /n/, as seen with [kanto]->[kãto].%0a%3c %0a%3c https://dialnet.unirioja.es/descarga/articulo/3269828.pdf%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
